-- Allianz Names Hartford’s Ramirez to Government Relations Job
-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   D e x h e i m e r
-- 2013-04-02T14:36:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-02/allianz-names-hartford-s-ramirez-to-government-relations-job.html
Allianz SE (ALV) , Germany’s largest
insurer, named Vanessa Ramirez as senior director of government
relations in the company’s North American life unit.  Ramirez previously worked at  Hartford Financial Services
Group Inc. (HIG)  and had worked for the office of former Connecticut
Governor Jodi Rell, according to a statement today from the unit
of Munich-based Allianz.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elizabeth Dexheimer in New York at 
 Edexheimer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
